#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kpat.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KPat (aka KPatience) is a relaxing card sorting game. To win the game a "
"player has to arrange a single deck of cards in certain order amongst each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"KPat (ali KPatience) (sl. pasjansa) je sprostitvena igra z urejanjem kart. "
"Za zmago v igri mora igralec zložiti en komplet igralnih kart v določenem "
"redu."

